&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;NO!!!&amp;nbsp; For all you anti-melee clerics out there,&amp;nbsp;you keep on believing that we melee/battle clerics want to tank mobs, that is simply not the case.&amp;nbsp; What we DO want is to add a little extra fun and challange to the game.&amp;nbsp; Typically that means adding DPS when we can and off tanking if and when we have to.&amp;nbsp; Besides that, try to answer these questions and see if you can justify your beliefs:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;Why would the Devs grant us&amp;nbsp;weapons like &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Noqufiel's Wand of Infinite Enmity&lt;/STRONG&gt; (caster ONLY) or &lt;STRONG&gt;Furious Hammer of Zek&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; (Cleric ONLY) or &lt;STRONG&gt;Delightful Orb of Forgotten Magic &lt;/STRONG&gt;(All/All) (These happen to be my last three primary weapons) or &lt;STRONG&gt;Illuminated Hammer&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;(again caster ONLY) &lt;STRONG&gt;Hammer of Holy Vengence&lt;/STRONG&gt; (cleric ONLY) and MANY others (from all over Norrath), if they did not intend for us to use those DD procs in melee combat?&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
